title: Most Transactions are Non-Market Transactions
categories: Economics
---

Aside from the thirty minutes each year that the two of you negotiate your salary, your relationship with your boss is hierarchical.

Even between coworkers, market transactions are beyond the pale of professional behavior. In high school, I worked at a local waterpark. Lifeguards, saddled with a shift in the middle of their family's summer vacation, would advertise the shift on a bulletin board in the breakroom. They would offer inducements